Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, we were able to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that you'd come, Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I think about it,\Nyou've always protected us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.27,0:02:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that you're our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you guys sure did pull one\Noutrageous stunt back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, to think that you shot\Nthrough the World Government's flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... it's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we did was take back a friend\Nwho was taken away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank You, Merry!\NSnow Falls over the Parting Sea"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, hey, hey! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? He isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he's calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, this isn't good. Without thinking, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! Come out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'm gonna beat the crap outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna beat the crap outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you know where Usopp is,\NSogeking? I can't find him anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry. He went back\Nahead of us on a small boat earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this ship actually belongs to him now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is it they need\Nin order to recognize Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we suspected, I can't find\Nanyone anywhere on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who on earth sailed this ship to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we definitely heard\Nthat voice calling out to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, someone most certainly called to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said all this time...\Nit was the Merry's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Merry?! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:05:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. There's no way a ship would talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda felt that way too, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way something\Nlike that... could happen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was a mystery to us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for some reason, these words\Nremained in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if this person actually\Nsaid it or I was imagining things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry you guys for a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may sound stupid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I feel that it might've been\Nan incarnation of the Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm crazy, don't you?\NYou don't have to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person looked like a sailor\Nholding a wooden hammer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...? Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw a Klabautermann.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Klabau...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klabautermann.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the legends known among sailors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more care the ship receives,\Nthe more it appreciates the sailors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship probably wanted to somehow\Ncarry you across to the other shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was able to encounter a crew\Nthat she wanted to carry so badly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that she'd borrow a human form to appear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she's been very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who talked to me then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was really you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a ship coming towards us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you guys're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Galley-La Company's ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They rushed out in Aqua Laguna and\Nstill made it okay! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They came back from Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahoy! Ice pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid-berg...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a crazy lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took on the World Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they really took everything back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Their ship is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on?!\NWhat happened all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of a sudden? Isn't this just natural?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was declared that Merry could no longer sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Merry is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:09:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops! This is bad! Merry is in trouble!\NPlease do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys... This is good timing!\NYou guys're all shipwrights, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you! Please do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's our friend who has been\Ntraveling with us all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just a bit ago she saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already done everything I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone on the scrap heap island?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this... the Straw Hats' ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The damage must've been caused by\NAqua Laguna. It's in a terrible state.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's beyond just damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to set sail one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no hope left for this ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there?!\NAnother big wave is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You want to set sail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is still stormy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go alone if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let you go out there all by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm watching a miracle right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:12:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A miracle of a ship that\Nhas long passed its limits...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been a shipwright for many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never seen a pirate ship this incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lived a splendid life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to the seas of adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then... are you guys ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry... The seabed is dark and lonesome,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll watch you to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was good that Usopp wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way... that he could bear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone must someday say farewell.\NThis is a man's parting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a single tear should be shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He, too... is prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for carrying us\Nfor such a long time, Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A caravel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day we'd play\Ncovered in mud until the sun set
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the Going Merry pirate ship is all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:02.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to abandon\Nthose innocent days we spent
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers to our new ship and crewmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:15.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm a dreamer, I'm still me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! The Merry\Ngot damaged quite a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When navigating a sailboat,\Neveryone has to participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,So things don't all have to fit\Ntogether like a jigsaw puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn it appropriately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Aw...\N--Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cannon practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:30.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as someone's "Yes"\Ncould be a "No" to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure don't fly good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, let me try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! You hit it on your first try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:40.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll surely always be free
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...! I really hit it on my first try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:55.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if tomorrow a wind passes\Nthrough and breaks the puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:58.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would blame you for that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Hey! That's my seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance to the Grand Line\Nlies ahead of that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to find the All Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:11.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a dream that day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:13.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our belief in ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to become a master swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to draw a world map!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:19.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,makes us able to cross the wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-In order... to become a\Nbrave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going... to the Grand Line!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:34.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We know the pain that\Nyou hold in your heart, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:38.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever depart this ship\Nand live in a different world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance to the Grand Line is a mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:53.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we can all surely smile
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the greatest sea in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! We're flying out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back! We're going straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me... join your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place for me to go or go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let me stay on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see... Then I guess\Nwe have no choice... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We continue to dream even today
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this ship's navigator?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrying the feelings you\Nentrusted with us as well
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! The ship is flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:23.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We once again cross these\Nrough seas and fight the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:34.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,So that our promise won't become a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:42.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And someday, to you who departed\Nour ship and live in a different world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:53.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll deliver the completed puzzle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to carry you even further.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to continue going on\Nadventures with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's us who have to apologize, Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good at steering...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I ran you into icebergs at times...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time I tore the sails, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro and Sanji are stupid,\Nso they broke all sorts of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp would fix them each time,\Nbut he isn't good at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's us who have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much... for taking\Ngood care of me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really have been happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because I had you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.74,0:22:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite an ordeal, but we're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The restoration of Water Seven starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... There seems to be a ruckus outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.18,0:22:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! The Navy is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Peace Interrupted! A Navy\NVice Admiral with a Fist of Love"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
